uture, which will strengthen and consolidate the role of the club and its continuous communication with the community.<br><br> Finally, the people of the area and their parents thanked Baniyas Club for bringing joy and happiness to the hearts of the children and all participants in the initiative, stressing the good organization and excellence of the initiative, which was co-organized by \"We are all police\" and who contributed to the success of the event and its distinctive appearance, in addition to all the sponsors and contributors who were one of  The most important reasons for success, whether through providing many facilities or by presenting various prizes and gifts, where the initiative witnessed the participation and contribution of the General Command of Abu Dhabi Police, the Ministry of Interior, the General Authority for Islamic Affairs and Endowments, the Abu Dhabi Center for Public Health, Abu Dhabi City Municipality, Abu Dhabi Islamic Bank, Fazaa Fund and Bawabat Al Sharq Mall  And Mediclinic.','','ip:31.215.55.139agent:Mozilla/5.0 (iPhone; CPU iPhone OS 15_3_1 like Mac OS X) AppleWebKit/605.1.15 (KHTML, like Gecko) Version/15.3 Mobile/15E148 Safari/604.1lang:en-US,en;q=0.9'),(612,'اكاديمية بني ياس تشارك في مهرجان الوحدة ','Baniyas Academy participated in Al Wahda Festival',1,'2022-03-30 00:00:00','e8775f8f26a26e8edcd3ca334c66f0ca.jpeg','مشاركة لاعبي أكاديمية نادي بني ياس مواليد 2013/2011 في مهرجان نادي الوحدة بوجود عدة أكاديميات ومدارس كروية تمثلت في وجود اندية الوحدة والظفرة والعين واكاديمية سوكر وباس ويوفنتوس وشتوتجارت .',' Baniyas Club Academy players, participated in the Al Wahda Club Festival, ages of ( born 2011/2013 ) in the presence of several football academies and schools represented by Al Wahda, Al Dhafra, Al Ain, Soccer Academy, Bass, Juventus and Stuttgart.','','ip:31.215.55.139agent:Mozilla/5.0 (iPhone; CPU iPhone OS 15_3_1 like Mac OS X) AppleWebKit/605.1.15 (KHTML, like Gecko) Version/15.3 Mobile/15E148 Safari/604.1lang:en-US,en;q=0.